Use these exact component variable names in App Designer. The code looks them up by property name on app, so the names must match exactly.

Minimum

 Update Animate_Style.Items to:
{'Stimulus', 'Dot', 'Map-FlashContourX', 'Map-SweepLine', 'Map-LoomingStimulus'}
 Keep these existing controls in place: Animate_Speed, Animate_LineAngle, Animate_XPosition, Animate_YPosition, Animate_End, Animate_MimicTrial
Mapping Controls

 Add Map_SettlePauseSec as a Numeric Edit Field, label Settle (s), default 5.0
 Add Map_FlashDurationSec as a Numeric Edit Field, label Flash Dur (s), default 0.5
 Add Map_InterFlashIntervalSec as a Numeric Edit Field, label Interflash (s), default 2.0
 Add Map_FlashCount as a Numeric Edit Field, label Flash Count, default 5
 Add Map_FlashXMin as a Numeric Edit Field, label Flash X Min, default -0.8
 
 Add Map_FlashXMax as a Numeric Edit Field, label Flash X Max, default 0.8
 
 Add Map_SweepXMin as a Numeric Edit Field, label Sweep X Min, default -1.2
 Add Map_SweepXMax as a Numeric Edit Field, label Sweep X Max, default 1.2
 Add Map_SweepSpeed as a Numeric Edit Field, label Sweep Speed, default 0.6
 
 
 Add Map_OrientedLineAngleDeg as a Numeric Edit Field, label Angle (deg), default 90
 
 Add Map_LoomX as a Numeric Edit Field, label Loom X, default 0
 Add Map_LoomY as a Numeric Edit Field, label Loom Y, default 0
 Add Map_LoomMinScale as a Numeric Edit Field, label Loom Min Scale, default 0.5
 Add Map_LoomMaxScale as a Numeric Edit Field, label Loom Max Scale, default 1.5
 Add Map_LoomPeriodSec as a Numeric Edit Field, label Loom Period (s), default 2.0
 Add Map_LoomVariant as a DropDown, label Loom Variant, items:
{'Correct', 'Incorrect', 'Alternate'}

 Add Map_DrawHz as a Numeric Edit Field, label Draw Hz, default 60
Fixation / Reward Controls

 Add Fix_Enable as a CheckBox, text Enable Fixation, default unchecked
 
 Add Fix_X as a Numeric Edit Field, label Fix X, default 0
 Add Fix_Y as a Numeric Edit Field, label Fix Y, default 0
 Add Fix_Radius as a Numeric Edit Field, label Fix Radius, default 0.03
 Add Fix_PeriodSec as a Numeric Edit Field, label Fix Period (s), default 2.0
 Add Fix_PeakThreshold as a Numeric Edit Field, label Peak Threshold, default 0.98
 Add Fix_RewardCooldownSec as a Numeric Edit Field, label Reward Cooldown (s), default 2.0
 Add Fix_RewardSide as a DropDown, label Reward Side, items:
{'Right', 'Left'}
 Add Fix_RewardEnable as a CheckBox, text Enable Fix Reward, default unchecked
Fastest Layout

 Put all Map_* controls in a new “Mapping” panel inside the animate area
 Put all Fix_* controls in a new “Fixation / Reward” panel below it
 Keep Animate_Style, Animate_Speed, Animate_LineAngle, Animate_XPosition, and Animate_YPosition where they already are
One important note: Map-SweepLine uses Map_OrientedLineAngleDeg or Animate_LineAngle to set orientation, so use 90 for a vertical line and 0 for a horizontal line.

